Talking to a sock, Mr Bob for socializing, checked. Will have lot of discussion and yelling.
Writing with body fluids on wall for writing, checked. You dont need paper or pen to write. Also you dont need free hands to draw. So you can be like "Look guards! No hands!".

snippet.textDisplay: Here's a twist: I spent 19 months of a 4 year sentence in AdSeg for a riot I didn't even participate in. Tbh, it's not that bad if you're ok with being alone. You can always talk to your neighbors either thru the door or thru the vents above your shower/toilet so you're not completely isolated. You get better food back there (the "high tech" or "solitary" part of the prison is usually in the back of the regular prison so we just called it "in the back") so you eat better. My time went pretty easily alone.
